  "detailed_description": "<strong>The Horror of Salazar House</strong> is a gothic, Italian horror inspired haunted house game with Virtual Boy style graphics and rotoscoped cut-scenes. <br>The debut game from Chilean developer Ignacio Maldonado.<br><br>Elisa, a young reporter, is sent to investigate the abandoned mansion of renowned author Jaime Salazar, who disappeared, along with his entire family in 1986. Setting out to find the truth of what happened in that house, she gets a lot more than she bargained for when she realizes the house of Salazar may not be totally abandoned...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/07d778a28f3488caa56c6d33a2bb4124.poster.avif?t=1669908453\" width=628 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/07d778a28f3488caa56c6d33a2bb4124.webm?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/07d778a28f3488caa56c6d33a2bb4124.mp4?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A retro point and click haunted adventure!<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>Choose a custom color pallet to emulate forgotten terminals and consoles<br></li><li>Playable in English, Spanish and Brazilian Portuguese.<br></li><li>Windows and Linux</li></ul><br>Can you solve <strong>The Enigma of Salazar House </strong> or will you become another permanent inhabitant?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/db8c47c687ce250399bbeb4ad64fa93a.poster.avif?t=1669908453\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/db8c47c687ce250399bbeb4ad64fa93a.webm?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/a7bb8be5856d9358817d03806457a933.poster.avif?t=1669908453\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/a7bb8be5856d9358817d03806457a933.webm?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/a7bb8be5856d9358817d03806457a933.mp4?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>The Horror of Salazar House</strong> is a gothic, Italian horror inspired haunted house game with Virtual Boy style graphics and rotoscoped cut-scenes. <br>The debut game from Chilean developer Ignacio Maldonado.<br><br>Elisa, a young reporter, is sent to investigate the abandoned mansion of renowned author Jaime Salazar, who disappeared, along with his entire family in 1986. Setting out to find the truth of what happened in that house, she gets a lot more than she bargained for when she realizes the house of Salazar may not be totally abandoned...<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/07d778a28f3488caa56c6d33a2bb4124.poster.avif?t=1669908453\" width=628 height=472 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/07d778a28f3488caa56c6d33a2bb4124.webm?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/07d778a28f3488caa56c6d33a2bb4124.mp4?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br> <br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A retro point and click haunted adventure!<br></li><li>Multiple endings<br></li><li>Choose a custom color pallet to emulate forgotten terminals and consoles<br></li><li>Playable in English, Spanish and Brazilian Portuguese.<br></li><li>Windows and Linux</li></ul><br>Can you solve <strong>The Enigma of Salazar House </strong> or will you become another permanent inhabitant?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/db8c47c687ce250399bbeb4ad64fa93a.poster.avif?t=1669908453\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/db8c47c687ce250399bbeb4ad64fa93a.webm?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/a7bb8be5856d9358817d03806457a933.poster.avif?t=1669908453\" width=600 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/a7bb8be5856d9358817d03806457a933.webm?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1405440/extras/a7bb8be5856d9358817d03806457a933.mp4?t=1669908453\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
